# Architecture Rules

Preferred architecture:
- Laravel 13
- PHP 8.3+
- Domain-oriented structure
- Service Layer
- Action Pattern
- Small focused classes
- Reusable UI systems

Prefer structure like:

app/Domains/
  Wallet/
  Inventory/
  Orders/
  Seller/
  Admin/

Avoid:
- fat controllers
- duplicated logic
- giant Blade files
- random helper logic
- mixed responsibilities



Always:
- inspect related files first
- preserve existing correct code
- explain architectural impact before changing behavior
